This is a working page that contains references to features that have been suggested for EAPI 6.

{{Note|The Gentoo Council has accepted EAPI 6 in its [https://projects.gentoo.org/council/meeting-logs/20151108-summary.txt 2015-11-08 meeting] and again, with one modification, in {{Bug|565700}} on 2015-11-13. The final wording can be found in the PMS document ([https://projects.gentoo.org/pms/6/pms.pdf PDF]). This page is kept for historical and documentation purposes.}}

The following list of features accepted for or rejected from EAPI 6 is based on Gentoo Council meetings of [https://projects.gentoo.org/council/meeting-logs/20140610-summary.txt 2014-06-10], [https://projects.gentoo.org/council/meeting-logs/20140617-summary.txt 2014-06-17], [https://projects.gentoo.org/council/meeting-logs/20140624-summary.txt 2014-06-24], [https://projects.gentoo.org/council/meeting-logs/20140909-summary.txt 2014-09-09], [https://projects.gentoo.org/council/meeting-logs/20141014-summary.txt 2014-10-14], and [https://projects.gentoo.org/council/meeting-logs/20141111-summary.txt 2014-11-11].

