*: [https://gitweb.gentoo.org/proj/pms.git/commit/?id=2b3637b42a5cdd911e6508213dee143c98406477 PMS wording]
*: {{Bug|449862}}

* Patch applying function in package manager
*: PMS wording [https://gitweb.gentoo.org/proj/pms.git/commit/?id=440b0ee22c50bfd1c7f0b1038213a282c8bbbfa8 1], [https://gitweb.gentoo.org/proj/pms.git/commit/?id=a8196cb8791b2eba41e27e9adae2c591fcefa04c 2]
